8 Research Toolkit (Requests to Assistant)\b0\fs22\line\bullet	ab Multi-source brief: “Summarize X from 3+ primary sources; list full citations.”\line\bullet	ab Regulatory guide (FR): “Outline the administrative steps for <topic> with official links.”\line\bullet	ab Data scan: “Find datasets for <topic> with license details and access method.”\line\bullet	ab Outline & angles: “Propose 3 angles and a 6-section outline for <story>.”\line\bullet	ab Multilingual support: “Translate this summary to FR and improve clarity for a general audience.”\line\line\b\fs28 Interop\b0\fs22\lineThis onboarding scroll links to the TGC-DAO Charter and will connect via tags to related governance and publishing artifacts.\line}